Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 30,000 human slaves we've \Ncaught in the sea over the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And 70,000 Fish-Men who know how to use arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They moved here from the \Nclosed Fish-Man District.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...100,000 outlaws altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how powerful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power that I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started this whole thing 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the late Queen of the Ryugu\N Kingdom, who you fools still love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime was killed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was not murdered by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, her kinsman, did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:05:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, standing in front of you now, killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:32.02,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Shirahoshi's Tears!\N Luffy Finally Shows Up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you already knew that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I killed your mother, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few years after it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megalo told me secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Megalo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megalo was owned by \NNeptune's army back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:07:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he witnessed everything that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi, why didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I told anyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone would hold a grudge \Nagainst Hordy-sama, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is not what Mother-sama wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:08:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last promise we made with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told us that no matter who did it to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should not get angry or hate anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let resentment or hatred \Nget the better of you for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did as Mother said \Nto do 10 years ago and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have been keeping this to yourself all\N this time, alone in the Hard Shell Tower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried not to harbor hate for\N the one who killed her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was her dying mother's wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's almost unthinkable someone \Nwould be able to keep such a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is such an obedient, admirable girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could have done such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it! Hey, Megalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had cried out right there, \Nyou could've drawn everybody's attention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let them know that I \Nwas the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So thank you for shutting your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for confiding\N only in this dumb girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were anybody else, \Nwe couldn't have come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Shirahoshi, \Nwhat you did was pretty stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call those\N actions in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you tried to stymie your \Nhate for me, this kingdom will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your father, your brothers, the citizens,\N and you yourself are all going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't listen to him, Princess-sama!\N You did nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was definitely foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King! Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama! Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how miserable they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great warriors?! Pathetic!\N They're barely alive now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Captain Hordy is so strong-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't make it until \Nthe time of execution-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good. They must \Nbe executed by beheading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only concern was Jimbei and\N Shirahoshi, and we got them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for us to wait\N until the appointed time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to execute these\N worthless creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They deserve death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They're really gonna kill\N Neptune the Great Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hell on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have 100,000 outlaws on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! When will the pirate with \Na hat come to destroy the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! When will it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. All I know is what\N will happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be tomorrow or a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they create havoc here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might be in trouble but those\N villains would be too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to come now, too! \NI don't want them to kill the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if they came now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to destroy the island,\N why don't you do it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your worst - right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Can you hear us, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hiding somewhere \Non the island, come here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic! \NThey're literally clutching at straws!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharley's previsions were always \Naccurate but this time, it's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How meaningless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools must be out of their minds.\N Let's bring them to their senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you stupid citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to proceed with the execution\N of the former king, Neptune - now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch very closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I cut former king Neptune's head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this half-assed king without a \Ndrop of racial pride will be gone forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the new kingdom of Fish-Men will rise,\N which will dominate the pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to the \Nshameless Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How regrettable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see that? He saved King Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And right before that,\N Princess Shirahoshi cried for his help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he come out of the shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he hiding in its stomach?! But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out already... But I \Nguess you had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much! What the... Who is he talking to-ch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We were ready\N from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we knew that Luffy would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sit tight as we had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage, release!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman appeared all of a sudden-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it, Jimbei-chan? \NThe letter from the Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Whoa! The letter is gone!\N When did she take it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I handed the key over to Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look up! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale and a lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is your chance! Go, Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes! Take the King and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that! Wait-zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it took the King and the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Give us back the royal family-gaban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Jimbei hatched a \Nplan with the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that he really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look how many people there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, are they all our enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so. It looks like \Nthere are 70,000 or 80,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, 100,000 of them, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go take a nap or something \Nif you want. I'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go wild, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the members of the Straw \NHats are coming out of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to destroy the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you occupy the Ryugu Palace?! \NDo you want to kill the royal family too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you guys who kidnapped the Mermaids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people friends or \Nfoes to the Fish-Man Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends or foes? That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll have to decide on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats have gathered \Nin the Conchcorde Plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hordy proclaims that he will \Nbecome King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sends the vast force of the New \NFish-Man Pirates to attack Luffy's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten pirates will battle to decide \Nthe fate of Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Big Clash! The Straw Hats vs.\N A Hundred Thousand Enemies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
